messages.msg1: A bird in the hand is worth two in the bush.
messages.msg2: Do. Or do not.  There is no try.
messages.msg3: If you want to test a man's character, give him power.
messages.msg4: In the end we only regret the chances we didn't take.
messages.msg5: It rubs the lotion on its skin or else it gets the hose again.
